783828927017,"type":"artifact_ready","data":{"artifact":{"id":"art-cmo","chiefId":"cmo","chiefTitle":"Chief Marketing Officer","title":"Launch Copy & Social Posts","format":"markdown","content":"# Launch kit — PocketLedger\n\n**Launch copy — PocketLedger (bold cut)**\n\n# Your bank account has feelings. Mostly fear.\n\nPocketLedger is the no-BS budget for people who've rage-quit three finance apps. Zero formulas. Zero shame spirals. Five minutes on Sunday and you're done being broke by accident.\n\n- **One page. The whole damage.** See it, own it, fix it.\n- **Five minutes, fr.** Less time than choosing what to watch.\n- **Nobody's watching.** No bank links. Your chaos stays private.\n\n---\n\n**Launch posts (bold cut)**\n\n**X / 1:** your budget app has 47 categories and you've opened it twice. PocketLedger: one page, five minutes, zero judgment. $12. go.\n\n**X / 2:** financial literacy is just knowing where the money went before it's gone. we made that take five minutes. you're welcome.\n\n**LinkedIn:** We built PocketLedger for the 70% who abandon budgeting apps in month one. One page. Five minutes a week. No shame mechanics. $12 at launch.","metrics":{"posts":3,"tone":"bold gen-z"}}}},{"seq":127,"runId":"run-mrh9mgb0-1","ts":1783828927017,"type":"agent_status","data":{"agentId":"cmo","status":"done"}},{"seq":128,"runId":"run-mrh9mgb0-1","ts":1783828927017,"type":"coo_narration","data":{"text":"Chief Marketing Officer delivered: Launch Copy & Social Posts."}},{"seq":129,"runId":"run-mrh9mgb0-1","ts":1783828927017,"type":"run_status","data":{"status":"delivering"}},{"seq":130,"runId":"run-mrh9mgb0-1","ts":1783828927017,"type":"agent_status","data":{"agentId":"coo","status":"thinking"}},{"seq":131,"runId":"run-mrh9mgb0-1","ts":1783828927017,"type":"agent_log","data":{"agentId":"coo","ts":1783828927017,"text":"Writing the executive summary"}},{"seq":132,"runId":"run-mrh9mgb0-1","ts":1783828929355,"type":"spend_tick","data":{"agentId":"coo","deptId":null,"costUsd":0.05,"deptSpentUsd":0,"deptBudgetUsd":0,"totalSpendUsd":1.253,"usage":{"input":4000,"output":2533}}},{"seq":133,"runId":"run-mrh9mgb0-1","ts":1783828929356,"type":"artifact_ready","data":{"artifact":{"id":"art-exec","chiefId":"coo","chiefTitle":"COO","title":"Executive Summary","format":"markdown","content":"# Executive summary — PocketLedger\n\n**What your company built today:** a complete launch package for a minimalist budgeting template aimed at young professionals who abandon traditional budgeting apps.\n\n**The wedge.** Research found a real gap: incumbents are either bloated systems or bare spreadsheets. PocketLedger owns *calm* — one page, five minutes on Sunday, no guilt mechanics.\n\n**The numbers.** Pricing locked per your Decision Desk call, with a base-case first-year projection near **$38k gross** (see the CFO's sheet for the exact figures behind the price you approved).\n\n**Go-to-market in one line:** launch to the burned-out majority — \"the budgeting template for people who quit budgeting apps.\"\n\n**Your next three actions:**\n1. Put the landing page live and connect a checkout link.\n2. Publish the launch posts (already cut in your approved tone).\n3. Complete the two legal checklist items flagged for the CEO — tax registration and business registration when revenue is real.\n\nEvery deliverable is on the shelf. Total agent labor for the whole company: on your Money panel, to the cent.","metrics":{}}}},{"seq":134,"runId":"run-mrh9mgb0-1","ts":1783828929356,"type":"agent_status","data":{"agentId":"coo","status":"done"}},{"seq":135,"runId":"run-mrh9mgb0-1","ts":1783828929356,"type":"run_status","data":{"status":"done"}},{"seq":136,"runId":"run-mrh9mgb0-1","ts":1783828929356,"type":"coo_narration","data":{"text":"The package is ready, CEO. Total agent labor: $1.25."}},{"seq":137,"runId":"run-mrh9mgb0-1","ts":1783828929356,"type":"run_done","data":{"totalSpendUsd":1.253,"durationMs":107072}}]}